{"tid":1510434,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好灰心","createTime":"2019-08-27T07:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:44:45.000Z","uid":203865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad945342aa5ec9b9ddd7000129dd6e1a05aa099","tid":1510434,"uid":203865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:36:26.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月黎，眼見住咁多不公平既事發生，黑警濫暴，三次百萬人大遊行，林鄭依然故我。突然覺得咩善有善報，惡有惡報都係扼人；屋企又有個覺得示威者做咩都唔啱既阿媽，實在令我好灰心。自問暫時未有勇氣做勇武，只係一個小小既和理非，每次見到有人受傷被害，心入面都十分痛心。林鄭同黑警既暴行罄竹難書，但依然可以逍遙在外，一諗到呢到就好無力。世界之巔倒，令我不堪負荷"},{"pid":"8326478bc13e6506a89644466bacb9e21ed4cfe9","tid":1510434,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"你覺得默字靚定墨字靚"},{"pid":"3bb03f2ffb0efdebf1aeea286b3c2df113026ca7","tid":1510434,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=d16239b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=b8626c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8biz2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=4f6281d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"64aaf31245bfb07ed271eb3fc125aca7a201ded9","tid":1510434,"uid":62318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"No god, No salvation<br />\n<br />\n依個就係一個做乜都得既世界，<br />\n冇人平衡，冇人阻止，只有時間會流逝<br />\n但係係宇宙時間既鴻流裡面，我地又只係微不足道既微生物<br />\n<br />\n人既價值，就係一個靈魂/意識，再加一個肉體<br />\n點樣發揮，全靠個體<br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得集合個體，成為一個意識，先係答案"}]}